Assignment:
1. Define a class named Circle which can be constructed by a radius. The Circle class has a method which can compute the area. 


2. Python program using class method and static method:
	a. Write a class method to create a Person object by birth year. 
	b. Write a static method to check if a Person is adult or not

3. Define a class named Shape and its subclass Square. The Square class has an init function which takes a length as argument. 
Both classes have a area function which can print the area of the shape where Shape's area is 0 by default.

4. Wrie an abstract class AbstractOperation having constructor for two operands and implement classes for operations addition, substraction and multiplication which inherits from abstract class.